  <brief_title>Use of Synvisc® in Knee Osteoarthritis - Medico-economical Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>Use of Synvisc® in Knee Osteoarthritis - Medico-economical Study (U.S.A.G.E. Médico-Economique)</official_title>
