  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The USAGE study aims at assessing on a long-term period (two years in average) the outcome in
      clinical or economical term of patients with knee osteoarthritis (OA) treated or not with
      Synvisc®, in the 1139.4 clinical trial.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
